{"tid":2158357,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何桂藍：極權下做異見者 坐監就係下場","createTime":"2020-08-15T16:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T10:48:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff9dbaf5e8b4e9eadb9da6b3df6a9430424d2a5","tid":2158357,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Dsl4MuF-ks9y260ZCVCANJIQX10=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J24GVHG6XVGXZEG5KJDXFSUJNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDsl4MuF-ks9y260ZCVCANJIQX10%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ24GVHG6XVGXZEG5KJDXFSUJNA.jpg&h=97926276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一場反修例運動，何桂藍放下記者證上議會戰場，在新東泛民初選以首名出線，旋即遭選舉主任DQ入閘資格，原定的立法會選舉更因疫情押後。進入議會抗爭夢碎，何桂藍未有後悔「落水」參選，未來會繼續在港記錄所見所聞，並投入公民社會、支援被捕者及民間研究工作，繼續向港人以至國際，揭露政權的不堪。<br />\n<br />\n原為《立場新聞》記者的何桂藍，去年7.21被元朗白衣人襲擊卻堅持直播，人氣急升，但決定「落水」參選，評價好壞參半。何桂藍接受《蘋果》訪問時直言：「過咗呢場選舉（初選），（「立場姐姐」）嗰個能量、知名度已經過咗去，而家喺我身上嘅係26,802票新東選民賦予畀我嘅一個責任。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/XWEXS2SARVCCJNVR66KYF26OKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FXWEXS2SARVCCJNVR66KYF26OKA%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL%2BrkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=7b1d38d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FXWEXS2SARVCCJNVR66KYF26OKA%2F&h=ab13cc1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/XWEXS2SARVCCJNVR66KYF26OKA/</a>"},{"pid":"b4b8ec2530b412aefc9a8bc8d5f53534ee23c5c2","tid":2158357,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\